CARRIAGE RIDES IN RICHMOND PARK - JUNE 2017
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    Experience the park like never before on a traditional carriage
    drawn by our majestic Shire horses. This magical 90 minute
    experience begins at Holly Lodge, Richmond Park, where you'll be
    met with summer refreshments.

    You will take your place in the six-seater Park Brake carriage,
    embarking on a 60 minute ride through the park in all its midsummer
    beauty! You'll also be treated to a unique behind-the-scenes visit
    of the working stables.

